snippet.title: Creature Packets - A game about cooking tiny creatures!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://kenforest.itch.io/creature-packets?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Creature Packets is a game about cooking tiny creatures. Using a microwave, you can bring creatures from packets to life.  Use blender to explore new substance packages to cook even more creatures.
